{
  "texts": [
    "Second, it uses dynamic masks.",
    "The BERT model gets a static mask during data preprocessing.",
    "The RoBERTa model uses dynamic masks: different mask modes are applied to different data sequences.",
    "Through this method, different masking methods can be learned by the RoB-ERTa model for different language representations after a large amount of data training.",
    "ALBERT [7]That the size of a model can have an impact on its performance is a lesson learned from the ongoing advances in language representation learning."
  ]
}